## 13. Reference: Folder Tree Walker

To find the SFMC UI folder path for any DE:

```powershell
$cur = <categoryId>
$path = @()
while ($cur) {
    $c = Invoke-RestMethod -Method Get `
        -Uri "$restBase/email/v1/categories/$cur" `
        -Headers @{ Authorization = "Bearer $token" }
    $path = ,$c.name + $path
    if (-not $c.parentCatId -or $c.parentCatId -eq 0) { break }
    $cur = $c.parentCatId
}
$path -join ' > '
```

Endpoints used:
- `/email/v1/categories/{id}` — single folder details
- `/data/v1/customobjects` — Data Extension CRUD
- `/data/v1/customobjects/{id}/fields` — DE field list
- `/automation/v1/automations` — automation list (status: `Ready` = active)

